----------------------------------------AMASS OWASP -------------------------------------------

Using Amass OWASP for reverse lookup network mapping tool used for api dns scraping etchttps://github.com/OWASP/Amass

Available on github 
 Amass 
 amass enum -d tesla.com -src -ip -norecursive -dir tesla     
-d domain , -src source ,-ip ip , -dir to which directory 

 amass intel  -whois -d google.com  -dir nameoffolder
 -whois look for whois database 


To see in visulisation the domain and all network in amass



---------------------------------------Sn1per----------------------------------------------------

Sn1per  its very vast tool and overwhelming

 sniper -t google.com

For open source information gathering and passive 

 sniper -t google.com -m stealth -o -re
-t target  -m mode -o osint -re recon

File stored in /usr/share/sniper/loot/workspace  for analysis all logs


